---
<footer id="footer-section" class="bg-ink text-cream mt-16 border-t-4 border-ink">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Brand & Tagline -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-lime">FreshDrive</h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-slate-300 max-w-sm">
          A dedicated tracker for entry-level, fresher, and government jobs across India. Hand-verified daily from company and PSU websites.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 font-sans text-sm font-semibold">
        <h3 class="text-lime uppercase tracking-wider text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-2">Platform</h3>
        <a href="#listings" class="hover:text-lime transition-colors">Browse Roles</a>
        <a href="#stats-section" class="hover:text-lime transition-colors">Sourcing Stats</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="hover:text-lime transition-colors">Sourcing Pipeline</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Disclaimers / Legal -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 font-sans text-xs text-slate-400">
        <h3 class="text-lime uppercase tracking-wider text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-2">Redirection Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          FreshDrive is an aggregator and links out directly to the original, official company career pages. We do not host in-house application forms or charge users. All copyrights belong to their respective company entities.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono">
          &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} FreshDrive. Built for graduates across India.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
